'''木星高能粒子探測儀'''（Jovian Energetic Particle Detector Instrument，JEDI）是進入[[木星|木星]]繞極軌道的[[朱諾號|朱諾號]]攜帶的儀器之一<ref name=haggerty>{{Cite web |url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2008AGUFMSM41B1683H |title=D. Haggerty, et al. - JEDI -- The Jupiter Energetic Particle Detector for the Juno mission (2008) |accessdate=2015-08-22 |archive-date=2018-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908005534/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2008AGUFMSM41B1683H |dead-url=no }}</ref>，它是用於研究[[木星的磁層|木星的磁層]]套裝儀器的一部分<ref name=haggerty/>。

JEDI的設計是用來蒐集"能量、光譜、質典型式（氫、氦、氧、硫）和角分配" <ref name=haggerty/>，這個計畫是研究能量和帶電粒子的<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2011/08/ula-atlasv-nasa-juno-jupiter/ |title=W. Grahm - ULA Atlas V launches NASA’s Juno on a path to Jupiter (2011) - Nasaspaceflight.com |accessdate=2015-08-22 |archive-date=2015-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911050845/http://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2011/08/ula-atlasv-nasa-juno-jupiter/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它可以檢測30-1,000,000[[電子伏特|KeV]]，而另一件儀器，JADE，可以觀測低於30KeV的能量<ref name=video>[http://missionjuno.swri.edu/media-gallery/instruments NASA - Video on JEDI] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928235011/http://missionjuno.swri.edu/media-gallery/instruments |date=2013-09-28 }}</ref>。正在研究的概念之一是，來自木星自轉的能量是否被轉化進入它的大氣層和磁層<ref name=video/>。

它是由 [[約翰·霍普金斯大學應用物理實驗室|約翰·霍普金斯大學應用物理實驗室]]（APL）建造<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jhuapl.edu/newscenter/pressreleases/2011/110805.asp |title=Space Scientists Seek Returns from JEDI |access-date=2015-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112225/http://www.jhuapl.edu/newscenter/pressreleases/2011/110805.asp |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，蒐集來自行星的極光磁場線、赤道磁層和極區電離層的硬輻射的''原位資料''<ref name=haggerty/>。目標之一是要了解極光，以及如何將粒子加速到如此高的速度<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.centauri-dreams.org/?p=19145 |title=P. Gilster -  Juno: Into the Jovian Magnetosphere - Centari Dreams |accessdate=2015-08-22 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923201834/http://www.centauri-dreams.org/?p=19145 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。木星的謎團之一是由兩極發出的X射線，但似乎不是來自極光環<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://science.nasa.gov/science-news/science-at-nasa/2002/07mar_jupiterpuzzle/ |title=Puzzling X-rays from Jupiter |accessdate=2015-08-22 |archive-date=2015-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919121936/http://science.nasa.gov/science-news/science-at-nasa/2002/07mar_jupiterpuzzle/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

